data.description:
WHAT A BEAUTIFUL HOME!  3 LEVELS + FULL BASEMENT 
(4 BD RMS, 2 WITH EN SUITE & FULL SITTING ROOMS, 4 FULL BATHS, 2 HALF BATHS).  

BASEMENT LEVEL = Laundry Room, Gym and Sauna Room. Full Great Room with Fireplace, Full Bathroom, Large Storage Room and Large Walk-In Closet.  Patio on Back with Entrance from Great Room & Gym.  

MAIN LEVEL =  Hardwood Floors throughout Main Level.  Custom Front Door with Custom Matching Window & Designer Rug, TV/Sitting Room,  Wrap around Deck on Back. Living Room with Fireplace with Deck Entrance, Master Bedroom with Tray Ceiling Entrance to Deck with Huge Master Bathroom with Double Walk-In Closets, Half (Guest) Bathroom.  Breakfast Nook with Tray Ceiling & Bay Window in Kitchen, Large Kitchen with Gorgeous Wood Cabinets, Formal Dining Room with Crown Molding. 

SECOND LEVEL = 2 Bedrooms with Ensuite & Sitting Rooms, Office/library.     

THIRD LEVEL = Bedroom with Built in Bookshelf, Walk-in Closet, Half Bathroom & Full Walk-in Attic Storage Room.  

2-Car Garage.  
PROPERTY  = 2.54 ACRES, HOME 4-SIDED BRICK.
data.whatILove: NOT IN SUBDIVISION.  SITS BY ITSELF ON NEARLY 3 ACRES.  ALL BRICK.  4 LEVELS
